{"id": 1641, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得国产喜剧作品逃不开哪些套路？", "description": "看了根本不会开心，只想为编剧团队的智力默哀。（题图：林小妖）", "record_count": 38218, "comment_count": 122, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170424141530INSOXvLwWUpKaH1d.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-22T17:00:19Z", "questions": [{"id": 2193, "title": "你觉得国产喜剧作品逃不开哪些套路？", "content": "你觉得国产喜剧作品逃不开哪些套路？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 194404, "content": "装疯卖傻，演技夸张", "image": "img/option/option/20170419233423gL3RHvwtqaYnA2Bi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 194405, "content": "使劲靠方言口音堆笑料，东北，广东和福建是重灾区", "image": "img/option/option/20170420000003xNTIFEy7YsLCP4ZA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 194406, "content": "趣味拙劣，段子核心不是“性”、“钱”就是“屎尿屁”", "image": "img/option/option/20170420000347GXcFnBKYNxtErwJ5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 194407, "content": "倒贴过时三年以上的网络流行语，“宝宝”、“也是醉了”", "image": "img/option/option/201704200015496WeYBuoD7V0lnHEp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 194408, "content": "没完没了的陈年老梗", "image": "img/option/option/20170420001813EbyCLlaDUTAFKWJs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 194409, "content": "取笑某一群体，例如残疾人、大龄未婚女性......", "image": "img/option/option/20170420002141nzcWvH3BXZm6V8fG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 194413, "content": "台词中强行抖机灵，塑造“金句”", "image": "img/option/option/201704200026567M5oFBuKVn9sLzRp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 204445, "content": "不合逻辑的广告插入，例如时髦金领用的却是联想？", "image": "img/option/option/20170517162319UDtmg4zi1Eo9q3e6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 204449, "content": "结局一定要生硬回归“爱”与“亲情”的主旋律", "image": "img/option/option/201705171610341wYnBKurhiN4oQpe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}